	<shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Misc/admin-datafiles.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;6:13">The Couchbase data files are in a <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Misc/admin-datafiles.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:1;6:58">var &gt; lib &gt; couchbase &gt; data</uicontrol> location 
