	<body class="- topic/body " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Misc/admin-datafiles.dita" xtrc="body:1;8:8">
		<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="/Users/Ruth/forks/docs-ng/dita/src/ag3/Misc/admin-datafiles.dita" xtrc="p:1;9:6">By default, Couchbase Server stores data files under the following paths:</p>
